---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Ultra Fast Broadband for Business — Hamilton & Waikato"
  description="Business-grade UFB fibre broadband packages with full installation and ongoing support from Central Communications Ltd in Hamilton and the Waikato."
>
  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-tag">Services — Broadband</span>
      <h1 class="page-title">Ultra Fast<br /><em>Broadband</em></h1>
      <p class="page-sub">Business-grade fibre internet with local support you can actually reach.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-grid">
        <div class="prose">
          <h2>Broadband Built for Business</h2>
          <p>
            Slow or unreliable internet costs your business money. Central Communications provides
            business-grade Ultra Fast Broadband (UFB) packages with full installation and dedicated
            local support — not an overseas call centre.
          </p>
          <p>
            As your internet provider, we take care of everything from the initial connection and
            router setup through to troubleshooting and ongoing support. And because we're also your
            data cabling specialists, we can make sure the connection gets to every part of your
            premises perfectly.
          </p>

          <h2>Why Choose Central Comms for Internet?</h2>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>Business-grade UFB fibre packages</li>
            <li>Local Hamilton support team</li>
            <li>Router &amp; equipment supply and configuration</li>
            <li>Integration with your phone system and CCTV</li>
            <li>Static IP options for businesses that need it</li>
            <li>24/7 emergency support</li>
            <li>Competitive pricing — ask for a quote</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Bundled Solutions</h2>
          <p>
            Many of our clients choose to bundle their internet with their phone system and/or CCTV.
            This simplifies billing, means a single point of contact for support, and often results
            in better overall pricing.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar">
          <div class="cta-box">
            <h3>Get a broadband quote</h3>
            <p>Tell us your address and requirements and we'll find the best package for you.</p>
            <a href="tel:+6480084800038" class="btn btn-ember">0800 848 0038</a>
            <a href="/#contact" class="btn btn-outline" style="margin-top:0.75rem;">Send a message</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-title { font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem); color: #e8f1ff; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem; }
  .page-title em { font-style: normal; color: #0ea5e9; }
  .page-sub { font-size: 1.1rem; color: #7ea3c8; max-width: 520px; }
  .content-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 340px; gap: 4rem; align-items: start; }
  .feature-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; }
  .feature-list li { padding-left: 1.5rem; position: relative; color: #b8cce0; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6; }
  .feature-list li::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 0.6rem; width: 6px; height: 6px; background: #0ea5e9; border-radius: 50%; }
  .sidebar { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; position: sticky; top: 6rem; }
  .cta-box { background: #0c1d35; border: 1px solid rgba(14,165,233,0.15); border-radius: 1rem; padding: 1.75rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }
  .cta-box h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; color: #e8f1ff; margin: 0; }
  .cta-box p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: #7ea3c8; margin: 0; line-height: 1.6; }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .content-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .sidebar { position: static; } }
</style>
